Relive the Organising Committee press conference
The Organising Committee for the 20th FIFA World Cup™ convened for its last session before the big kick-off on 5 June in Sao Paulo. 
The press conference is available to view in full on 
.  
FIFA President Blatter, the Minister of Sports Aldo Rebelo, the Chairman of the Organising Committee of the FIFA World Cup Eugenio Figueredo, the President of the Local Organising Committee Jose Maria Marin and FIFA Secretary General Jérôme Valcke all attended. 
  
